{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_ling_set_1", "eventName": "醒時夢長", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "醒時夢長", "storyInfo": "初到尚蜀，為了尋一處僻靜地小睡，半醉的令來到這山巔古亭。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g09_teahouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.8, "loop": "true", "channel": "bse"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老哥，你的爛肉麵，趁熱！", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "燙燙燙！", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位客官，您要的歸行老酒只剩了半壇，再說這酒烈了些，這是小店新到的湖松酒，前晌剛啟窖，您看......", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#7$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#7$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "向來是客挑酒，幾時有酒挑客？這尚蜀的規矩，未免與別處不同。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#7$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這新酒可能解渴？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能。湖松酒清甜滑喉，入口綿長——", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能醉人？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#3$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就要看您喝多少了，是酒都能醉人。", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不知，你見我醉了，不再上就是。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（欸，不像本地人啊。）", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（看她的打扮和氣度，想必是哪個富貴人家遊山玩水，來尚蜀尋消遣吧。）", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（話說，我這幾天連著做同一個夢......）", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（那我昨天還夢見和小慧成親了呢！）", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（趕緊吃你的爛肉麵，別耽誤上工。）", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說來聽聽。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#3$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呀，客官，我們瞎嘀咕，打擾您喝酒了。", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_140#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獨飲無聊，我請你喝酒，你把夢說與我聽。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_140#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是......解夢師嗎？我聽說大炎別的地方有專門幫人解夢的行當。", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_140#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_140#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我權當給您解個悶吧。", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這幾天，好幾次夢到附近天災頻發，人心惶惶，天師府連降多道權杖，任命我為總督造，負責尚蜀移動城市的改建。", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信使找到我的時候，我正在雕石頭——", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_140#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "改建移動城市？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#3$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_140#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。您一路來應該已經發現了，尚蜀的移動城市是與別處不同的。", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_140#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將群山挪移至移動平台，這在其他地方無法想像，尚蜀的移動城市可謂巧奪天工。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_140#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正因為這樣，我們的承重也超出了常規移動平台的好幾倍，機動性大打折扣。", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是老天護佑，尚蜀人傑地靈，極少有天災，移動城市自建成起並未真的移動過，它還真不一定經得起檢驗。", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_140#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有幾分道理。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_140#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那個夢！我在那個夢裡找到了解決的辦法！", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當上總督造後，這個著急啊......突然在泡茶時得到了啟發。", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大炎江河連川，百川又歸海，這四通八達的水路本身便是移動城市天然的運行軌道。", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "況且，常言道“水可載舟”，水流還能與移動城市的動力系統結合，解決承重過大而機動性不足的問題。", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "試想，若天災突降，百年山城卻輕如羽毛，快如長箭，順江而遷。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "百姓安坐在家中煮茶，只是偶爾風起浪捲，打濕了三山十八峰，晴空大雨，才恍然發現不知不覺間已去千里。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "到那時，尚蜀將真正不畏天災，民生安泰。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒真是個壯觀的夢！我那個妹妹要是在，想必又能得一幅新畫。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈你這個夢唯一真實的地方就只有雕石頭！", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別的怎麼就不真了？", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "改建移動城市......你這是把自己當土木天師了啊。", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒也無妨。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "土木天師，想來最開始，也是要從這樣的夢做起的。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰又想雕一輩子石頭呢......難道你想當一輩子夥計？", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（噓！當心點，別讓我們掌櫃的聽到。）\t", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我覺得挺好的，客人們來來去去，五湖四海的，有趣得很。雖然起早貪黑，苦是苦了點，但逢年過節，掌櫃的也不曾虧待了我們。", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "存一存，等過個一年半載，我說不定就能把小慧娶回家了。", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你可得抓點緊。小慧雖然家境一般，但長得好看，我可聽說已經有人向她提了親......", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "錘子——哪個不開眼的。", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈哈！", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過說不定你真的能當上土木天師呢......", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這夢要成了真，那就不是蜀道難，而是蜀道通了。到時我們山城的石雕和茶葉能賣到大炎的任何地方。不，不光是大炎。", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說了半天，忘了問解夢師我這個夢到底怎麼回事了。連著做，總覺得不太尋常......", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並未說自己會解夢。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也只是常做夢而已。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要想聽，我也可以......", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那還是——", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，已經過了你平時上工的時辰了，趕緊把帳結了回去。", "name": "酒館夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呀！", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呀！今天來得急，身上沒帶......", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一併算在我的酒資裡，也不能白聽你一個夢。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這怎麼好意思......", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多打聽一個事，這尚蜀三山十八峰，哪一處最幽僻，最稱得上“蜀道難”的說法？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是要？", "name": "石匠"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "酒喝夠了，想尋個安靜地方睡上一覺，興許也能做個如你這般有趣的夢。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g06_mountainroad_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "書生夢馬簪金花，女娥夢橋生紅藥，世人所謂“夢”者，發乎事，起乎情。那個石匠的夢，也是此理。"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢是好夢，但以為它關乎吉凶，隨隨便便做了，卻不敢隨隨便便解。"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢終究只是夢，過往將來，終是由己。"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#3$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們怎麼在此？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#3$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spiritwhoosh"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_143#2", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘎......", "name": "墨魎"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是夕讓你們這些小傢伙來迎我，還是我已然入了她的畫中......", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#3$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_143#2", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘎嘎......", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#3$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抑或......我只是有了醉意？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛說到哪兒了？", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說你羡慕我。", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們這些小傢伙居然會說話......", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，湖松酒都有這般後勁，下次該試試歸行老酒。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "墨兄，想來這天地間，和我殊途同歸的，也就只有你了。但你終歸要比我自在得多。", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是哪兒的話？", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "器皿本是死物，無心無念，只不過意外受到令的點染，化成了倀。", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "缺柄少蓋的茶壺，生出來的倀同樣缺胳膊斷腿。薄薄青瓷的倀，同樣耐不住幾下摔打......", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倀的形與意，都局限在器皿本身了。本體怎樣，我們便只能怎樣。", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也同樣只存在於夕的畫卷之中，未必就算得上“活物”。", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夕的畫卷，已然是另一方天地了......你們雖然是隨筆塗鴉而成，但和那畫中的無限風光一樣，都是夕的“念想”啊。", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“念想”是最無拘束的。有形的時候，一葉扁舟，千江疊浪，枯樹生花，華髮再青，天地顛倒，萬象迷離。", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你從哪兒知道的這些詞......", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無形的時候，滴墨不染，擱筆留白，都自有意義。", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夕的念想不停，畫卷不收，你們便永遠自由自在。", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽得出來你著實羡慕啊。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘎嘎，器兄，我反倒覺得你才值得羡慕。", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自由自在，未見得就是好啊。", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我問你，這裡好幾隻墨魎，你能分得清哪隻是夕喜悅時所塗，哪隻是夕傷懷時所塗嗎？", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你們都長得差不多。", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對啊，我們甚至不知道，夕在塗抹我們時，是何種心情，或者她就是......無情無感。", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可拿你來說吧，你通體古褐色，但肚腹黢黑，那是沖茶煮茶十多年留下的茶漬。你還沒靠近，我就彷彿聞到了茶香。", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詩畫之倀附庸風雅，兵戈之倀嗜好殺伐，水火不侵的倀，我們便知它的本體必然經受過長久的火煉窯燒。", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們生來便有根可循，是限制，可未嘗不是歸宿，這正是你們的意義啊。", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "見器倀便能見器物本身，更能見使器物的人。甚至器倀雖死，器物本身卻還在。", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而墨魎呢，只是無根的風，吹過來晃過去。夕不喜不安時，便能把畫都撕了，更何況那畫上的幾抹塗鴉。", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "器兄，這樣無根的自由，你還羡慕嗎？", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我依然覺得......", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣吧，我們誰也辯不過誰，正好令在這，請她做個評斷吧。", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "令不要偏袒就是了。", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們總算想起我了......爭得口渴了吧？我這邊還剩幾罈子湖松酒，正好解渴。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_143#2"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（咕咚咕咚）", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#2"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（咕咚咕咚）", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸你別吐啊！", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咽不下去咽不下去，喉嚨燒得慌，我滴個天爺。", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夕是不飲酒的，她怕睡著了做夢......那小墨魎你也應該喝不了吧？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_143#2"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（咕咚咕咚）", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#2"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有呀，我覺得挺好喝的，清甜滑喉，入口綿長。", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#2"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暈乎乎的，像是夕翻轉了畫......難怪都說炎國人喜歡這玩意兒。", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#2"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈，確實是個好東西。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我甚愛酒，南方的桃梅晚釀喝過，北方的烈刀子也喝過，可受我點染的器倀，卻連一口酒都咽不下去。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "滴酒不沾的夕，她所畫的墨魎偏偏覺得此味甚妙。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們可有所思？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "器倀&墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們確實是我和夕的造物，得了幾分形意。但幾分的我，便已然不是我了，二者終究是有區別的。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "器倀非器，墨魎非墨。你們，難道不都是自己嗎？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "器倀&墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再者，到底何謂“自由”？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們覺得我和夕是否自由？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_143#2"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "令自然是自由的——", "name": "墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_143#2"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎......", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道不是？", "name": "器倀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不知。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真自在者，不知何為自在。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們越是苦苦糾結，越是不得其解。本就是自在之物，又何苦自尋煩惱？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "器倀&墨魎"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是不解？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呀，既然不解，索性都散了吧，別擋了路。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_306_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_143#1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spiritwhoosh"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "浪費了我幾口酒......", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#7$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "常言道“蜀道難”，果然不虛。盤旋回折，聳峭入雲，山路轉彎，竟又是一段山路。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也罷，想來到山巔時，正好一場好眠。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "playSound", "attributes": {"key": "$tactfulboost", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_landscape", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來又是一場詩會。"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白瓷的杯子順水而下，杯中酒與泉流渾然一色。酒杯停在誰處，即須成詩三句。筆力不逮者，銜杯作揖，是謂“流觴”。"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "酒是桃梅晚釀，採早開的桃蕊，與存好的晚梅一併搗碎入酒，清冽甘甜，入口生津。"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那酒的滋味，妙絕。"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope02_intro", "key": "$newhope02_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "採菱的少女把滿滿一兜菱角倒進船艙，卻不留神將船槳踢飛了出去，脆生生的呼叫聲傳出去數里遠。"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "春夏之交的雨下了半月還未停，在石板路上砸起的霧氣渺若輕煙，相鄰的人家隔著雨幕抱怨說廳堂幾時能乾燥些。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好茶者鬥茶，好酒者鬥酒，好釣者鬥釣，富者鬥金玉，貧者鬥鳴蟲......"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦對了，還有燈會，那可比流觴熱鬧得多了，造型各異的花燈從街的這頭燃到那頭，逢著佳節更是徹夜不滅。"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "移一步可得一句，看一景可得一詩，所以那些年的詩會，我從未輸過。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一江煙水一芰荷，酒招深處浣清波。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒臥西山翠，千年醒回舟。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "世情旖旎，酣醉酩酊，何妨衰病減心情。"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盡興嗎？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盡興。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盡興是盡興，可就是太容易盡興了。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "厭倦一樣事，便對百樣事都覺得新鮮。只是這新鮮到頭，終究還是厭倦。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "令，這裡不是你的歸宿。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何不聽我的，走得遠些去看看。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你所謂“春風不至”的地方？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#6$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#6$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又有什麼不同？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#6$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去了便知。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#6$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡便是我的歸宿了？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不知。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "流觴詩會少一個令不少，多一個令不多。可我讓你去的地方，需要你。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許你在那裡，才能寫出，新的詩來。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_laccolith", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那座移動城市。"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那座橫在大漠前的移動城市。"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使數百年過去，我依然記得初見它時的震撼。此刻，我竟然又站在了它的城樓上。"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大漠綿延千里，風沙蒸騰起熱浪，雲煙浩渺，我能感受到皮膚在急速失去水分。"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了控制水源，它在建造時並未考慮佔據險要地勢，依山脈以為屏障，而是臨近草甸和湖泊。"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如此一來，乾燥的風掃過無遮無擋的大漠，直撲在城牆上。它像個孤獨的巨人，巍巍然矗立在天地間，身無可依。"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "旌旗漫捲，長河落日。"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城關外，戰士們正將昨日死難兄弟的屍體搬運出來，一排排放好，我挨個走過，將他們的眼睛闔上。"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨日的連場血戰猶在耳畔。遮天蔽日的箭，晴空似夜，殺聲如裂帛，經久不絕。"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火炬在他們身下點燃，無人哀哭，因為新的戰鬥將近。煙塵滾滾，但迅速被風吹進茫茫大漠。"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詩酒已然幫我忘卻了許多我曾厭倦的東西，可在此般景象面前，我反應過來時，卻已重新握緊了武器。"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為身邊的每一個將士，都握緊了武器。"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不能讓那些傢伙，靠近身後的大炎。那是他們的家鄉，那裡有他們的親人。"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "橫在這茫茫大漠前的，不是這座巨人般的移動城市，而是這城裡的將士。"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孤城聽征鼓，年歲莫問，但憑豪氣多。"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰言將軍有死志，故壘新柳年年生。"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說的沒錯......我是應該來此的。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g07_fairyland_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你竟然也來了，看來真是夢了。", "name": "令"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（無言的轟鳴）", "name": "“歲相”"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別吼了，我方才喝了幾罈子湖松酒，頭暈著哩。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#6$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（無言的轟鳴）", "name": "“歲相”"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#6$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "逃避？非也。我既不是年，也不是夕。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（無言的轟鳴）", "name": "“歲相”"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好好好，那我且問你。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#7$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覬覦這天地，又可知這偌大天地間，到底有什麼？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#7$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（無言的轟鳴）", "name": "“歲相”"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#7$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可知蒙壟的新茶，該是在三月採，還是四月採？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可知大漠長夜苦寒時，常唱什麼歌，常飲什麼酒？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你又可知......", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "“歲相”"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對這天地，一無所知。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，你即是我......", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "枉我們自詡活了這千百年，卻依然有太多不知不聞的事，不解不曉的情。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（無言的轟鳴）", "name": "“歲相”"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也曾像山腳酒館裡的那個石匠，連做夢也有憂戚，或者如我那妹妹一樣，連夢都不敢做了。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也曾像器倀和墨魎，覺得受限於自己，又受限於天地，總不自由。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這些活了千百年的造物，傲視幾十年壽命的芸芸眾生，笑他們活得愚昧。歸根結底，還是我們更蠢一些。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "“歲相”"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從南而北，再到這蜀道山巔，於我而言，只不過是一場酣夢。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實，從太古以來，經過的時間，行過的地方，千年萬年，無非是更大的一場夢。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一場大夢做罷，我終於知我是誰——", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（無言的轟鳴）", "name": "“歲相”"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "罷了，說了你也不懂。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既不懂，還不走？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既是我的夢，怎麼解由我，醉也由我，醒也由我。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "playSound", "attributes": {"key": "$tactfulboost", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g08_pavilion", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我既醒來，你又焉在？", "name": "令"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "25_i05", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醒來。"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "酒也空了。"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好一場夢啊。"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看見了什麼？"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "落日燒透半天的雲，三山十八峰，漫漫蜀道，觸手即是煙霞。這景色，不曾入畫，也不曾入詩。"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看見了什麼？"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "流觴詩會，瓷杯停在了一人又一人面前。漠上長亭，孤煙裡，千百人擊鼓遠征。"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既見縱情逍遙的我，也見求全求解、不求甚解的我。夢只是夢，我之為我，都快意。"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明是在這攥江峰頂，無名空地，卻彷彿看見了整個大炎。不，是整個太古以來，縱橫四方，都如風掠過身側。"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "見山卻問石，臨淵而忘水，原是如此。此地不如就叫“忘水坪”吧。"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彷彿......還看見了年和夕。呵，既然夢中未見，想必夢外，很快也將再見的。"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......日盡水長去......雪落月空留。", "name": "令"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}